(BAKER MCKENZIE \(BANGKOK\)  PROPOSAL FOR LEGAL SERVICES) Tj T*
(Re: Project Delta  Acquisition of a packaging manufacturer in Vietnam) Tj T*
(To: SCG Legal, Outside Counsel Sourcing) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. UNDERSTANDING OF THE MATTER) Tj T*
(SCG Packaging Public Company Limited intends to acquire 100% of the shares of a) Tj T*
(privately held packaging manufacturer headquartered in Binh Duong Province,) Tj T*
(Vietnam. The engagement covers legal due diligence, transaction documents,) Tj T*
(regulatory and merger filings, and closing support.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. TEAM AND STAFFING) Tj T*
(Lead partner: 1 M&A partner resident in our Ho Chi Minh City office, supported) Tj T*
(by 1 tax partner \(Bangkok\). Core team: 2 senior associates and 1 associate in) Tj T*
(HCMC. Dedicated deal team with partner-led negotiation sessions. We have closed) Tj T*
(14 manufacturing acquisitions in Vietnam over the past five years, including 3) Tj T*
(in Binh Duong Province.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. FEES) Tj T*
(Total fee: USD 220,000, capped, exclusive of disbursements and VAT.) Tj T*
(Phase breakdown:) Tj T*
(- Legal due diligence: USD 75,000) Tj T*
(- SPA drafting and negotiation: USD 80,000) Tj T*
(- Regulatory and merger filing: USD 40,000) Tj T*
(- Closing: USD 25,000) Tj T*
(Fee type: capped fee with carve-outs for competition filings above two) Tj T*
(jurisdictions and tax structuring outside Vietnam and Thailand.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. ASSUMPTIONS AND EXCLUSIONS) Tj T*
(Assumes a data room of no more than 3,000 documents and a single signing and) Tj T*
(closing. Excludes post-closing integration, employment restructuring beyond) Tj T*
(transfer advice, and disputes.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. AI DISCLOSURE) Tj T*
(We use AI-assisted document review for due diligence \(Relativity plus) Tj T*
(proprietary tools\). All output is reviewed by qualified lawyers.) Tj T*
